    "If a i ∈ { think, answer, cite }, the output ζ i is appended to the context, forming s i+1 = s i ⊕ ⟨a i, ζ i ⟩.",
    "If a i = tool, the model executes the tool call, receives o i = T k (q i; α i), and updates the state as s i+1 = s i ⊕ ⟨a i, ζ i, o i ⟩.",
